
'''Veronica Bekoe''' yɛ abdoedeɛ mu nyansapɛfo a ofiri Ghana. Ɔyɛ Veronica Bokiti kɔfabae a ne botae ne sɛ wɔde betu nsanyareɛ ase.

== Nhomasua ==
Veronica kɔɔ suapɔn a ɛne Kwame Nkrumah University of Science and Technology (KNUST) ma no nyaa abɔdin krataa wɔ abɔdeɛ mu nyansapɛ  ho wɔ afe 1968 kosi 1972.

== Nnwuma ==
Veronica ne adwumakuo a ɛne Ghana Health Service ayɛ firi 1972 kosi 2008, a n’adwumayɛbea ne amansan apowmuden hwɛfo ne beaeɛ a wode mfidie yɛ nipadua mu nhwehwɛmu. Ɔsan nso yɛ onipa titriw a na ɔhwɛ ɔman no AIDS ne nna mu nyarewa ho nhyehyɛi so

== Nea otumi yɛe ==
Wonim Veronica sɛ ɔno ne Veronica Bokiti no farebae. Bokiti no boatae ne sɛ wɔde bɛboa ama watu nyarewa te sɛ Cholera ne ayamtuo yareɛ ne nyarewa afoforo ase. Wɔ afe 2020 mu no, Bokiti no bɛyɛɛ ade titriw wɔ Afrika aman mu sɛnea ɛbɛyɛ na w’tumi ako atia amansan yareɛ kodiawuo a ɛne Coronovirus (COVID-19) anaa SARS-COV-2.
